name: Haribo x Suede 'Poppy Red'
story: Releasing as part of a larger collection with the German candy brand, the Haribo x PUMA Suede ‘Poppy Red’ dresses the classic model in a flooded crimson finish. ‘HARIBO’ is stamped on the lateral heel of the soft suede upper, while dual PUMA and Haribo branding lands on the stitched tongue tag and sockliner. The confectioner’s signature Goldbear gummy appears via a molded hangtag, a gel insert on the heel tab, and a subtle graphic print throughout the translucent rubber outsole.

Jordan 6 Retro Gold Hoops (W)
story: The women’s Air Jordan 6 Retro ‘Gold Hoops’ adds gilded accents to the shoe that Michael Jordan wore when he clinched his first ever NBA championship. The vintage mid-top carries a white tumbled leather upper with Barely Rose hits on the tongue, heel tab and midsole, fitted with a visible Air-sole unit in the heel. Metallic gold lace locks are matched by a trio of earring-inspired gold hoops, with a Jumpman charm attached to the lowest ring via a short gold chain. Underfoot, milky translucent rubber is utilized on the outsole.

KAWHI 'New Money'
story: Taking its design cues from a crisp $100 bill, the New Balance KAWHI ‘New Money’ continues a bankroll-inspired series that began with the ‘Money Stacks’ colorway of the New Balance OMN1S. Kawhi Leonard’s signature shoe features a muted teal upper constructed from mesh with a synthetic forefoot overlay. Gold accents make their way to the sneaker’s Kinetic Stitch quarter panel, a raised NB logo on the prominent heel counter, and ‘100’ stamped atop the tongue. The sneaker rides on a FuelCell foam midsole, supported by a full-length performance plate and a translucent rubber outsole.

name: adidas NMD R1 Crystal White Clear Pink (W)
Reebok Question Low White Clear Blue Sole
story: The Reebok Question Low ‘White Clear’ updates Allen Iverson’s debut signature shoe with a blank-slate finish. Ghillie lacing secures the white leather upper, reinforced with a tonal leather toe cap and accented with a Question logo stamped on the heel tab. Breathable mesh is utilized on the sneaker’s throat, while soft textile lines the low-cut collar. The sneaker rides on a matching white EVA midsole with visible Hexalite cushioning. Underfoot, an icy translucent rubber outsole provides grippy traction.

adidas Superstar LEGO White Black
story: The LEGO x adidas Superstar ‘Base Plates’ transforms the iconic sneaker with unique details inspired by the Danish toy brand. The low-top makes use of a synthetic white leather upper made in part with recycled content. Reminiscent of a LEGO baseplate, a studded texture is applied to the sneaker’s rubber toe, as well as the contrasting black heel tab and serrated three-stripes. Dual adidas and LEGO branding adorns the bright yellow sockliner. The low-profile silhouette is mounted a standard rubber cuposle, featuring a herringbone traction pattern underfoot.

name: Air Force 1 '07 LV8 'Coconut Milk Hyper Royal'
Nike Space Hippie 01 Melon Tint Aquamarine
story: Continuing the brand’s exploratory footwear collection predicated on recycling and limited resources, the Nike Space Hippie 01 ‘Melon Tint’ spotlights the speckled Crater Foam midsole — built with a blend of standard foam compounds and Nike Grind rubber — by applying a vibrant orange finish. Up top, the sneaker’s beige knit construction is made with mostly recycled content that includes plastic bottles, T-shirts and post-industrial scraps. A plush insole composed of ZoomX foam scraps delivers a cushioned ride.

name: Nike Space Hippie 01 Obsidian
story: Releasing as part of a sustainable line designed to lower the brand’s carbon footprint, the Nike Space Hippie 01 ‘Obsidian’ carries a navy blue knit upper made with ‘Space Waste Yarn,’ which includes recycled materials like T-shirts, fabric scraps and plastic water bottles. The sock-like build is mounted on a cream-hued Crater Foam midsole, which works in tandem with a plush sockliner constructed from ZoomX foam scraps — the same cushioning technology used on Nike’s pinnacle NEXT% running shoes.

Reebok Freestyle Hi Power Rangers Pink Ranger (W)
story: Releasing as part of a larger collection inspired by the ‘90s superhero franchise, the Power Rangers x Reebok women’s Freestyle High ‘Pterodactyl Zord’ gives the nod to the Pink Ranger’s battle vehicle. The high-top trainer utilizes a pink leather upper with white side stripes and a metallic silver heel overlay. ‘Pterodactyl’ is printed on the top ankle strap on the left shoe, while the left features text that reads ‘It’s Morphin Time.’ Underneath the straps, mismatched tongue tags reveal the Power Rangers’ lightning bolt logo and a pterodactyl graphic.

story: Launching as part of a larger collection celebrating the television superhero series from the ‘90s, the Power Rangers x Reebok Zig Kinetica 2 ‘Dinozord’ takes inspiration from the battle craft piloted by the Red Ranger. The training shoe makes use of a crimson textile upper with a forefoot overlay ringed in a silver dinosaur tooth detailing. Mismatched tongue tags display the Power Rangers’ yellow lightning bolt and an illustrated Tyrannosaurus graphic. In terms of performance, the lightweight build is mounted on a responsive Floatride Fuel midsole with sidewalls arranged in a dynamic zigzag configuration.
